        <num>47-4-28</num>
        <content>
          <p>The board shall keep permanent records of all its accounts in granting retirement benefits and shall keep proper records and books concerning its operation. Each year at the beginning of the regular session of the General Assembly the board shall present an annual financial statement of the fund.</p>
          <p>(Ga. L. 1969, p. 998, ยง 14.)</p>
